---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about Kitchen Explored — honest kitchen appliance comparisons for home cooks.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Kitchen Explored</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg">We help home cooks make confident purchasing decisions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-navy prose-a:text-orange-start">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Kitchen Explored helps home cooks cut through marketing noise and find the kitchen tools that
        actually deliver. We write detailed, side-by-side comparisons of blenders, cookware, knives,
        ovens, pressure cookers, faucets, and more.
      </p>
      <h2>How We Test</h2>
      <p>
        Every comparison is based on hands-on testing in real kitchens. We focus on the factors that
        matter most to everyday cooks: performance, durability, ease of use, and value for money.
      </p>
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Kitchen Explored was founded by Matt Hickman, a home cook and kitchen enthusiast who got tired
        of vague product reviews. Since 2018, we've published over 180 appliance comparisons to help
        people buy smarter.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
